      <div class="view-footer">
      <h3>About me</h3>
<p>I am making complementary currency <a href="http://drupal.org/project/mutual_credit">software</a>, and keeping the organisation I co-founded, <a href="http://communityforge.net">Community Forge</a>, ticking over, and relaunching the <a href="http://ccmag.net">CC Mag</a>. I work my arse off and live by gifts as much as possible.

</p><p>Check out my <a href="http://matslats.net/complementary_currencies">Cc software blog</a>.</p>

<p>Google <a href="http://www.google.ch/search?q=matslats">matslats!</a>.</p>    </div>
  
  
